{
  "texts": [
    "It must be accurate, dependable, reproducible and safe, with a backup plan.",
    "That is the only method to reduce and prevent unintentional injury.",
    "• Privacy and data governance: In addition to privacy and data protection, data governance procedures must consider data quality and integrity and legitimize data access.",
    "• Transparency: Data, systems and AI business models should be transparent.",
    "Traceability methods aid in this."
  ]
}